1.7.1	You can configure the Bizhub to have a static IP address through the menu on the printer itself.	St
1.7.2	It is like this with every single network printer we have in my office (around 35 right now).	St
1.7.3	We have a bizhub 350 and it did come w/ software but you need to assign the static IP via the menu ON the printer (should have a little LCD screen or touch screen).	St
1.7.4	Set it to whatever IP you would like (so long as it is not conflicting w/ another IP address on the network).	St
